 presence, Luke."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "TAUNTING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Being perceptive is cool, non?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "WATCH_OUT_BADASS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " [shakes head]"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SHAKE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Except that time when you missed Lea's speech module malfunction."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "WONDERING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Shush. That happened once, ok?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "SUSPICIOUS"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 9", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Did you two \\c[3]go for a walk\\c[0]?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "DETERMINED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Jap. Also jumped from cliffs and boring metal pipes."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Bashed some mobs along the way too."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "LAUGH"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ..."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Not that, silly.\\. You know, what I meant."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " A \\c[3]date\\c[0]!"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "DETERMINED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Sure. I gave Lea a tour of the place once."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "DEFAULT"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " A tour? Of a place you've hardly been to for a week?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "CURIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": "  Why not?\\. Tours are my speciality."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "EYES_CLOSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " And there was awful lot of nothing to do anyway."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "SKEPTICAL"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Sounds like you."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "EMBARRASSED"}}]}, {"type": "IF", "withElse": false, "condition": "call.runCount == 10", "thenStep": [{"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Did you two \\c[3]kiss\\c[0]?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "DETERMINED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...W-what?!!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "EX2_EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " That escalated quickly..."}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "WHISTLING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " ...W-why?!"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "EX2_EMBARRASSED"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " I'm a detective, remember?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "SMILE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " \\c[1]Did you kiss or no?"}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "DEAD_INSIDE"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Can evotars even do that?"}, "person": {"person": "main.luke", "expression": "WONDERING"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Wait."}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "ANGRY"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " Why are you looking at me?\\. I thought you were an expert."}, "person": {"person": "main.emilie", "expression": "CURIOUS"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " \\c[1]WAAAAAAAAIT!!\\c[0]"}, "person": {"person": "main.lea", "expression": "SHOUT_PANIC"}}, {"type": "SHOW_SIDE_MSG", "message": {"en_US": " .\\..\\..\\.O-okay.